{"tid":2517275,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"新西蘭國會認定新疆維吾爾人權被侵犯 中方堅決反對","createTime":"2021-05-05T08:26:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-05T08:41:17.000Z","uid":230530,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"8a0c1470cba98709be4ac03ea5bcc46dc38f7e54","tid":2517275,"uid":230530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T08:26:24.000Z","msg":"新西蘭國會通過涉及中國新疆的動議，一致認定維吾爾族人權被嚴重侵犯，但未有使用種族滅絕一詞。 動議由行動新西蘭黨提出，為了爭取總理阿德恩領導的工黨支持，刪去種族滅絕一詞，最終議會各方予以通過。外長馬胡塔強調，已多次就新疆問題向中方提出關切，但種族滅絕是國際罪行中最嚴重的罪行，只有在根據國際法嚴格評估後，才可作出正式的法律認定。 <br />\n<br />\n中國駐新西蘭大使館批評新西蘭議會罔顧事實真相，執意通過涉疆動議，無理指責中方違反人權，是粗暴干涉中國內政，中方強烈不滿和堅決反對，希望新西蘭議會多做有利中新友好的事，而不是相反。"},{"pid":"f24d4ad901b469ace0005f59b657824c03ff8c88","tid":2517275,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T08:39:21.000Z","msg":"以為新西蘭盲咗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200529/343085926668439553.jpeg/22k_lbtPASBRITebo9O3VUmBslrveBRv19b3WdfW91k?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200529%2F343085926668439553.jpeg%2F22k_lbtPASBRITebo9O3VUmBslrveBRv19b3WdfW91k%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=d33f65e3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"adf301e25caa84da3f8da61d0ced75a0e280a8b2","tid":2517275,"uid":306914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T08:40:23.000Z","msg":"彈出彈入，識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e221a9e4fe950c1dd78edb3b72453456803ef979","tid":2517275,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"adf301e25caa84da3f8da61d0ced75a0e280a8b2","tid":2517275,"uid":306914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T08:40:23.000Z","msg":"彈出彈入，識玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-05T08:41:17.000Z","msg":"但都跪左少少 因為阿德恩隻賤閪唔比用種族滅絕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class